                    <div class="absolute -top-32 -right-20 w-[30rem] h-[30rem] bg-cyan-500 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[120px] opacity-40 animate-pulse"></div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-40 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[140px] opacity-40"></div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute -right-16 top-10 text-[20rem] text-cyan-400 opacity-10 -rotate-12 pointer-events-none" data-icon="robot_2">robot_2</span>

                    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl backdrop-blur-md bg-white/5 p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400/20 to-indigo-400/20 text-cyan-300 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6 border border-cyan-400/30">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(34,211,238,1)] animate-pulse"></span>
                            Keunggulan VeinTech
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 via-white to-indigo-300 mb-4 leading-tight tracking-tight">Efisiensi Operasional hingga 80%</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg">Kami menekan biaya operasional dan mempercepat proses bisnis Anda melalui otomatisasi AI cerdas yang bekerja 24/7 tanpa henti.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 w-full lg:w-auto flex justify-start lg:justify-center">
                        <a href="/portfolio" class="group/btn relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 text-slate-950 font-bold text-lg overflow-hidden transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(34,211,238,0.5)]">
                            <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-white/20 group-hover/btn:translate-x-full transition-transform duration-500 ease-out -translate-x-full skew-x-12"></span>
                            Lihat Studi Kasus
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-950/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Slide 2: Integration (Emerald/Teal Mesh) -->
                <div class="min-w-full flex-shrink-0 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#022c22] via-[#064e3b] to-[#0f172a] p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12 h-auto lg:h-[24rem]">
                    <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-[25rem] h-[25rem] bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[120px] opacity-30 animate-pulse"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[30rem] h-[30rem] bg-teal-600 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[140px] opacity-40"></div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute left-1/2 top-10 text-[24rem] text-emerald-400 opacity-5 rotate-12 pointer-events-none" data-icon="hub">hub</span>

                    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl backdrop-blur-md bg-black/20 p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-emerald-400/20 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-emerald-400/20 text-emerald-300 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6 border border-emerald-400/30">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(52,211,153,1)] animate-pulse"></span>
                            Integrasi Tanpa Batas
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-300 via-white to-teal-200 mb-4 leading-tight tracking-tight">Satu Ekosistem untuk Semua Aplikasi</h2>
                        <p class="text-emerald-50/80 text-lg">Jangan biarkan data terperangkap dalam silo. Kami menghubungkan CRM, ERP, dan aplikasi terpisah Anda ke dalam satu alur yang harmonis.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 w-full lg:w-auto flex justify-start lg:justify-center">
                        <a href="/services/integrasi-sistem" class="group/btn relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-500 text-slate-950 font-bold text-lg overflow-hidden transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(52,211,153,0.5)]">
                            <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-white/20 group-hover/btn:translate-x-full transition-transform duration-500 ease-out -translate-x-full skew-x-12"></span>
                            Pelajari Integrasi
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-950/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="account_tree">account_tree</span>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Slide 3: Security (Ruby/Rose Mesh) -->
                <div class="min-w-full flex-shrink-0 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4c0519] via-[#27000b] to-[#171717] p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12 h-auto lg:h-[24rem]">
                    <div class="absolute top-10 right-20 w-[24rem] h-[24rem] bg-rose-600 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[120px] opacity-40 animate-pulse"></div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-20 left-20 w-[28rem] h-[28rem] bg-red-700 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[140px] opacity-30"></div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 text-[26rem] text-rose-500 opacity-5 -rotate-12 pointer-events-none" data-icon="shield_locked">shield_locked</span>

                    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl backdrop-blur-md bg-rose-950/30 p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-rose-500/20 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-300 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6 border border-rose-500/30">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-rose-400 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(251,113,133,1)] animate-pulse"></span>
                            Perlindungan Enterprise
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-300 via-white to-red-300 mb-4 leading-tight tracking-tight">Standar Keamanan Zero Trust</h2>
                        <p class="text-rose-100/80 text-lg">Perlindungan data level elit. Sistem Anda kebal terhadap kebocoran dan selalu mematuhi pedoman UU PDP terketat.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 w-full lg:w-auto flex justify-start lg:justify-center">
